87
00:05:48,070 --> 00:05:50,470
I invite you to rest in the outer palace too.

88
00:05:50,770 --> 00:05:52,490
You may enter the palace tomorrow.

89
00:05:52,490 --> 00:05:53,290
Outer palace?

90
00:05:55,950 --> 00:05:56,810
Sect Leader Li,

91
