115
00:06:41,780 --> 00:06:42,350
Yes.

116
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,100
Those four craftsmen

117
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:46,830
only listened to the demon monk's orders.

118
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,490
The child bugs probably

119
00:06:48,490 --> 00:06:51,220
helped the Demon Monk find that abandoned garden.

120
00:06:51,220 --> 00:06:53,140
It means that the mother bug is nearby.

121
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:54,140
But the Demon Monk

122
00:06:54,340 --> 00:06:56,800
wanted the four craftsmen to search for him.

123
00:06:56,820 --> 00:06:57,480
He probably

124
00:06:57,820 --> 00:06:59,700
only confirmed this general direction.

125
00:06:59,700 --> 00:07:00,260
So,

126
00:07:00,490 --> 00:07:02,850
we have to look for the rest.

127
00:07:03,340 --> 00:07:04,140
You mean

128
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:06,420
those four craftsmen know where the mother bug is?

129
00:07:06,420 --> 00:07:07,510
Did you notice

130
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:10,690
the four craftsmen have no beard?

131
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:15,920
Come on, don't just eat.

132
00:07:16,170 --> 00:07:17,360
Come, drink up.

133
00:07:17,410 --> 00:07:18,160
Don't just eat.

134
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,270
Alright, cheers.

135
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:22,420
Who are you?

136
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:23,750
Just a doctor.

137
00:07:23,850 --> 00:07:25,290
A doctor?

138
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:27,740
