We'll start working soon,

142
00:07:36,780 --> 00:07:38,380
so we all came out for a drink.

143
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:39,840
Here.

144
00:07:40,130 --> 00:07:40,570
Here.

145
00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:46,520
Keep an eye on them.

146
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,260
Make sure nothing goes wrong.

147
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,570
They come every day,

148
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:54,490
[Wang Tong]

149
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:53,880
but it's been so long.

150
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,280
How can I remember clearly?

151
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,520
Whenever I enter the abandoned garden,

152
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:58,050
[Li Fei, Lu Fang, Zhao Chi]

153
00:07:56,970 --> 00:07:58,330
I think of our old place.

154
00:07:59,530 --> 00:08:00,170
How about

155
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:01,520
we find a way to escape?

156
00:08:02,820 --> 00:08:03,820
Watch your mouth.

157
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,660
[White Jade Academy]

158
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:24,940
Lord Yang.

159
00:08:25,340 --> 00:08:26,650
Sect Leader Li, don't act rashly.

160
00:08:26,650 --> 00:08:28,910
The Wansheng Clan has their eyes on here.

161
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,640
I've found out the backgrounds of the four men.

162
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,640
As you expected,

163
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:34,440
they were eunuchs in the palace over ten years ago.

164
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,980
They are now living in different places.

165
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:37,580
The Wansheng Clan found them

166
00:08:37,890 --> 00:08:40,940
and sent them to the palace as craftsmen of the Ministry of Industry.

167
00:08:40,940 --> 00:08:42,070
Why were the eunuchs

168
00:08:42,690 --> 00:08:44,090
kicked out of the palace?

169
00:08:44,539 --> 00:08:46,340
They committed crimes of theft.

170
00:08:47,179 --> 00:08:48,140
They stole?

171
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:50,920
Shouldn't they be executed?

172
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:52,220
That's the strange part.

173
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:53,180
Many precious items

174
00:08:53,180 --> 00:08:54,690
were found on them at the time,

175
00:08:54,690 --> 00:08:55,720
but they insisted

176
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:58,620
they found it from a corpse in the wasteland.

177
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:00,870
When the Imperial City Division went to investigate,

178
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:02,570
they indeed found a corpse.

179
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:05,300
Its body was broken and limbs were incomplete.

180
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:07,060
It couldn't have been caused by humans.

181
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:09,100
It was more like a tiger or wolf that caused it,

182
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:11,020
but the Beast Garden is outside the palace.

183
00:09:11,020 --> 00:09:13,620
How could wild beasts come to the inner palace?

184
00:09:13,660 --> 00:09:16,190
There were indeed treasures around the body.

185
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,920
Their testimonies became credible.

186
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:22,340
Was the one who died also a palace eunuch?

187
00:09:22,970 --> 00:09:23,480
Yes.

188
00:09:24,970 --> 00:09:26,210
In that case,

189
00:09:27,150 --> 00:09:29,550
I think the five committed theft together,

190
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:32,140
and killed one due to the uneven distribution of spoils.

191
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:34,120
Master suspected that as well,

192
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:37,060
but the treasures found were not in this dynasty's style.

193
00:09:37,060 --> 00:09:38,860
Rather, they were from 100 years ago.

194
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:40,200
When treasures in the palace were checked,

195
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,730
nothing was found missing.

196
00:09:42,410 --> 00:09:43,620
Without any evidence,

197
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:46,020
they could only kick them out of the palace.

198
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:47,700
Treasures from 100 years ago

199
00:09:47,710 --> 00:09:48,900
suddenly appeared

200
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:50,580
next to a corpse.

201
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:52,350
Don't you think that's strange?

202
00:09:52,350 --> 00:09:53,760
Do you know where exactly

203
00:09:54,050 --> 00:09:55,450
the treasures came from?

204
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:57,880
It's hard to trace the gold and silver,

205
00:09:58,490 --> 00:10:01,240
but there was a jade Buddha statue

206
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:03,370
received by Emperor Guangqing as tribute 100 years ago.

207
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:06,130
It is said to be worshiped in the Pagoda of Bliss.

208
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:10,710
The Pagoda of Bliss?

209
00:10:10,890 --> 00:10:13,740
I heard from Empress Dowager that

210
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:16,900
Emperor Guangqing built it to pray for a son,

211
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:20,580
but His Majesty said it’s not true.

212
00:10:21,180 --> 00:10:22,180
It's just a rumor.

213
00:10:22,650 --> 00:10:23,980
Does the Pagoda of Bliss

214
00:10:24,110 --> 00:10:26,090
really exist or not?

215
00:10:26,730 --> 00:10:28,820
According to the old people in the palace,

216
00:10:28,820 --> 00:10:31,240
Emperor Guangqing had no children back then.

217
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:33,300
Later, the Pagoda of Bliss was built.

218
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:37,010
Consort Ying soon became pregnant with a prince and became the empress.

219
00:10:37,010 --> 00:10:37,850
But somehow,

220
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:40,730
the Pagoda of Bliss vanished overnight.

221
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:42,210
Vanished?

222
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:43,080
Yes.

223
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,480
In one night,

224
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,790
not a single piece of tile remained

225
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:49,510
where the pagoda originally stood.

226
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:55,480
The Pagoda of Bliss?

227
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:57,180
The Pagoda of Bliss is missing!

228
00:10:57,180 --> 00:10:58,790
The Pagoda of Bliss is gone!

229
00:10:58,820 --> 00:11:01,600
The palace forbade it from being mentioned afterward.

230
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,730
It became a mystery.

231
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:05,570
Legend has it that this pagoda contained heavenly fortune.

232
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:07,010
After the fortune was exchanged for a prince,

233
00:11:07,010 --> 00:11:08,870
the heavens took the pagoda back.

234
00:11:08,890 --> 00:11:10,270
But everyone in the palace

235
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:12,190
knew the pagoda had been built.

236
00:11:12,570 --> 00:11:14,570
There must be clues left behind.

237
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,640
There is no record in the palace.

238
00:11:17,980 --> 00:11:18,520
However,

239
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:19,930
back then,

240
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,720
I found a draft of a pagoda

241
00:11:22,050 --> 00:11:25,180
in the hands of Eunuch Wu, who served Emperor Guangqing.

242
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:30,570
Eunuch Wu loved poetry.

243
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:33,090
The picture was inside a book.

244
00:11:33,610 --> 00:11:34,180
But...

245
00:11:34,430 --> 00:11:36,630
I don't know if it's the Pagoda of Bliss.

246
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:14,790
Look.

247
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:17,040
The Pagoda of Bliss.

248
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:20,540
The mother bug is hidden in the missing pagoda.

249
00:12:21,470 --> 00:12:25,320
Why did Shan Gudao search for these four eunuchs?

250
00:12:25,730 --> 00:12:27,260
Because these four eunuchs

251
00:12:28,140 --> 00:12:29,870
had gone to the Pagoda of Bliss.

252
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,400
We can't escape.

253
00:12:39,730 --> 00:12:41,820
How about we tell them?

254
00:12:42,710 --> 00:12:44,240
You're not afraid of dying?

255
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:46,310
It can't follow us forever.

256
00:12:55,450 --> 00:12:56,250
Monster!

257
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,630
Help! There's a monster!

258
00:12:58,740 --> 00:12:59,820
Monster!

259
00:13:00,820 --> 00:13:01,460
Ghost!

260
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:03,320
What monster?

261
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:05,760
Ni Tianhou appeared again!

262
00:13:07,740 --> 00:13:08,580
Don't kill me!

263
00:13:08,710 --> 00:13:09,650
I didn't say anything.

264
00:13:09,650 --> 00:13:10,970
I didn't say anything.

265
00:13:11,590 --> 00:13:12,520
What did you say?

266
00:13:12,740 --> 00:13:14,140
Who is trying to kill you?

267
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,970
These men said Ni Tianhou is back.

268
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:20,640
Have you

269
00:13:21,490 --> 00:13:22,950
