282
00:14:17,780 --> 00:14:18,910
A hundred years ago?

283
00:14:19,530 --> 00:14:20,900
Is it really a ghost?

284
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:22,050
The design is old,

285
00:14:22,220 --> 00:14:23,420
but the fabric is new.

286
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:25,120
This robe contains

287
00:14:25,420 --> 00:14:26,940
a putrid smell.

288
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:29,510
It must be the smell of beast blood.

289
00:14:29,620 --> 00:14:30,350
It seems

290
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:34,350
someone is playing tricks behind the scenes.

291
00:14:34,740 --> 00:14:36,400
It's the Wansheng Clan again.

292
00:14:37,300 --> 00:14:38,760
What I don’t understand is

293
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:40,910
the Wansheng Clan found these four people

294
00:14:40,910 --> 00:14:42,770
to search for the Pagoda of Bliss.

295
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:44,940
But then,

296
00:14:44,940 --> 00:14:46,590
why would they cause a commotion?

297
00:14:46,590 --> 00:14:49,590
Shan Gudao said I tried my best to get words out of them.

298
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,470
He must think

299
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:54,480
that I'm behind this bloody robe and beast.

300
00:14:56,180 --> 00:14:58,600
It seems there's a third person behind this.

301
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,500
Who is he?

302
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:01,740
Why did he do this?

303
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,710
It was Li Lianhua.

304
00:15:12,660 --> 00:15:14,700
He deliberately splashed water in the daytime

305
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:17,430
but actually froze the child bugs with snow salt.

306
00:15:17,620 --> 00:15:18,950
Now he got a bloody robe.

307
00:15:19,380 --> 00:15:20,470
We can't get rid of him.

308
00:15:20,470 --> 00:15:21,820
He's very difficult to deal with.

309
00:15:21,820 --> 00:15:22,820
Should I kill him?

310
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:24,400
-No.
-Don’t ruin the plan.

311
00:15:24,810 --> 00:15:26,010
We can't kill him now.

312
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:28,030
He showed his face to the emperor.

313
00:15:28,030 --> 00:15:29,150
If we kill him now,

314
00:15:29,290 --> 00:15:30,550
we'll alert the enemy.

315
00:15:30,820 --> 00:15:31,900
He is no longer the Li Xiangyi

316
00:15:31,900 --> 00:15:34,020
who commanded the martial arts world before.

317
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:34,780
Where did he

318
00:15:35,330 --> 00:15:37,650
get this expensive snow salt?

319
00:15:38,190 --> 00:15:39,400
We haven't found the mother bug,

320
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:40,580
but the child bugs died.

321
00:15:40,580 --> 00:15:42,290
Those four idiots don't dare to tell us

322
00:15:42,290 --> 00:15:43,530
where the entrance was.

323
00:15:43,530 --> 00:15:45,390
How do we find the Pagoda of Bliss?

324
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:48,430
We'll use some means to force them to speak tomorrow.

325
00:15:48,900 --> 00:15:50,300
We can't wait any longer.

326
00:15:51,710 --> 00:15:52,900
[White Jade Academy]

327
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:58,520
[East Hall]

328
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:19,690
What?

329
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:23,400
You still can't tell which area is the best?

330
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:24,270
Well,

331
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:26,180
we need to look further.

332
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:28,100
We need to check more carefully.

333
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:29,340
Eunuch Wang,

334
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:33,370
to prevent evil disturbances when the soil is moved,

335
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:38,460
put these black-iron flags in the corners of the abandoned palace

336
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:40,180
to suppress the evil spirits.

337
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:41,220
That's great.

338
00:16:41,610 --> 00:16:42,180
Let's go.

339
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:51,580
Since I brought you all in the imperial city,

340
00:16:51,740 --> 00:16:54,000
it means I know everything about you all.

341
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:56,980
Starting today, I will kill

342
00:16:57,660 --> 00:16:59,060
one of your family members

343
00:16:59,060 --> 00:17:00,100
each day

344
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:01,790
until you speak.

345
00:17:01,810 --> 00:17:03,210
Please spare us.

346
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:05,400
There really is a monster!

347
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,460
People will die if we speak nonsense.

348
00:17:10,010 --> 00:17:11,780
If you tell the truth,

349
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:13,540
you will die.

350
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:16,079
If you don't tell me,

351
00:17:17,460 --> 00:17:19,660
both you and your family will die.

352
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:22,260
Lu Fang,

353
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:24,740
you still have

354
00:17:24,740 --> 00:17:27,339
an 80-year-old mother waiting for you at home.

355
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:27,940
I...

356
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:29,140
Do you want her to die?

357
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:31,069
How do you want her to die?

358
00:17:31,260 --> 00:17:31,940
Beheaded,

359
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,960
drowned in the river,

360
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:36,060
or dismembered?

361
00:17:36,570 --> 00:17:37,580
Tell me.

362
00:17:38,330 --> 00:17:39,130
Don't kill me.

363
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:40,460
I know nothing.

364
00:17:40,460 --> 00:17:40,900
Spare me!

365
00:17:40,900 --> 00:17:43,140
Ni Tianhou eats people who steal from the Pagoda of Bliss.

366
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:44,370
Where else do you want to escape to?

367
00:17:44,370 --> 00:17:46,180
I entered the Pagoda of Bliss with the others.

368
00:17:46,180 --> 00:17:47,070
I am not the main culprit.

369
00:17:47,070 --> 00:17:47,850
Don't kill me.

370
00:17:47,850 --> 00:17:49,900
-Don't kill me!
-Where is the Pagoda of Bliss?

371
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:50,370
It's...

372
00:17:55,100 --> 00:17:56,580
Physician Li.

373
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:01,320
What happened?

374
00:18:01,970 --> 00:18:02,810
Physician Li,

375
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:04,070
didn't you get sick?

376
00:18:04,110 --> 00:18:05,370
Why are you here again?

377
00:18:06,060 --> 00:18:07,700
I gave myself some medicine.

378
00:18:07,980 --> 00:18:09,380
I'm much better now.

379
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:11,990
Thank you for helping me request for leave.

380
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:15,250
You don't care about your health,

381
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:17,690
but you always trouble yourself.

382
00:18:18,210 --> 00:18:19,740
Thank you for your concern.

383
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:44,160
It's troublesome recently.

384
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:45,280
My opponents are always

385
00:18:45,280 --> 00:18:47,460
those who've become well-known decades ago.

386
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:50,520
Crazy Knife, Fatal Five Fists, and Bone-gnawing Spear

387
00:18:50,660 --> 00:18:52,790
are each more difficult than the last.

388
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:53,780
Who's next?

389
00:18:54,620 --> 00:18:56,480
I'll continue to accept the duel.

390
00:19:08,370 --> 00:19:09,500
Xiangyi Swordplay.

391
00:19:10,710 --> 00:19:12,970
This is the sword of Li Xiangyi’s Master.

392
00:19:19,370 --> 00:19:21,540
I have to go against Li Xiangyi's master.

393
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:22,620
You will never win

394
00:19:23,490 --> 00:19:24,890
this final battle.

395
00:19:50,540 --> 00:19:51,060
No.

396
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:53,240
I can't get through this.

397
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:54,150
Give up.

398
00:19:56,250 --> 00:19:57,650
I'm not Li Xiangyi.

399
00:19:58,520 --> 00:19:59,920
I can't defeat Qi Mushan.

400
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,860
There will always be a new legend.

401
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:06,630
Maybe

402
00:20:08,290 --> 00:20:10,140
you'll be the next new legend.

403
00:20:15,700 --> 00:20:18,300
The Xiangyi Swordplay and Yangzhouman are compatible.

404
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:20,220
The internal energy forms the structure of the sword technique.

405
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:22,830
The sword technique is the soul of the internal energy.

406
00:20:22,830 --> 00:20:24,980
Li Xiangyi's martial arts had accumulated

407
00:20:24,980 --> 00:20:26,430
since childhood.

408
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:28,310
That's why his body and soul were unified

409
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:29,490
and he could move freely

410
00:20:29,490 --> 00:20:30,700
to defeat his master.

411
00:20:33,910 --> 00:20:36,360
What about me?

412
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,630
Where is Shan Gudao?

413
00:21:37,090 --> 00:21:37,890
Take him down!

414
00:21:47,050 --> 00:21:48,930
What kind of martial arts is this?

415
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:54,100
The newly created Mr. Worried's Swordplay.

416
00:21:54,650 --> 00:21:55,780
Let me ask you again.

417
00:21:56,260 --> 00:21:57,390
Where is Shan Gudao?

418
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:58,630
I don't know.

419
00:22:03,420 --> 00:22:04,460
Master...

420
00:22:04,540 --> 00:22:05,870
Master is in the palace.

421
00:22:07,100 --> 00:22:08,500
He went to the palace too?

422
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:10,310
Li Lianhua...

423
00:22:13,610 --> 00:22:17,480
[Palace]

424
00:22:19,490 --> 00:22:22,470
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

425
00:22:25,090 --> 00:22:28,220
[Harmonious Breeze]

426
00:22:31,020 --> 00:22:33,660
[Together]

427
00:22:50,310 --> 00:22:51,170
Sect Leader Li.

428
00:22:51,620 --> 00:22:52,220
Thank you.

429
00:22:53,550 --> 00:22:55,950
I didn't expect Shan Gudao to be so skilled.

430
00:22:55,990 --> 00:22:58,590
If he hadn't restrained himself in the palace this morning,

431
00:22:58,590 --> 00:22:59,850
he would've caught us.

432
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:00,840
How is it?

433
00:23:01,300 --> 00:23:02,830
Did you get anything today?

434
00:23:03,270 --> 00:23:04,920
Did the four of them not return?

435
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:07,080
Didn't they leave the palace with you?

436
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:10,390
The craftsmen had to do roll-call with the Ministry of Industry,

437
00:23:10,390 --> 00:23:11,720
so they were taken away.

438
00:23:11,900 --> 00:23:13,230
It seems that Shan Gudao

439
00:23:13,850 --> 00:23:15,710
wanted to hide these four people.

440
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:16,380
Lord Yang,

441
00:23:16,780 --> 00:23:20,540
does the Ministry of Industry have a special station in the inner palace?

442
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:22,880
The inner palace is for the imperial family.

443
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:25,280
How could the Ministry of Industry be here?

444
00:23:25,460 --> 00:23:26,390
However, there is a Shanyi Workshop

445
00:23:26,390 --> 00:23:28,290
where various materials are stored,

446
00:23:28,290 --> 00:23:30,220
but it's not a place for people to live in.

447
00:23:30,220 --> 00:23:33,280
These people were planted by the Ministry of Industry.

448
00:23:33,580 --> 00:23:35,980
They must be hidden in the Shanyi Workshop.

449
00:23:36,040 --> 00:23:38,500
I don't think Shan Gudao can wait any longer.

450
00:23:38,520 --> 00:23:40,420
That's why he's doing everything he can

451
00:23:40,420 --> 00:23:42,690
to find the whereabouts of the Pagoda of Bliss.

452
00:23:42,690 --> 00:23:44,350
I must be one step ahead of him.

453
00:23:53,710 --> 00:23:54,380
Who are you?

454
00:23:54,410 --> 00:23:57,140
I wish to see Dian Qiu, Imperial Guard Commander.

455
00:24:02,500 --> 00:24:03,660
I am Dian Qiu.

456
00:24:04,020 --> 00:24:04,780
You are?

457
00:24:16,460 --> 00:24:18,260
I can only bring you to the palace,

458
00:24:18,260 --> 00:24:20,420
but I can't guarantee you can walk around freely.

459
00:24:20,420 --> 00:24:21,660
There are many hidden guards in the palace.

460
00:24:21,660 --> 00:24:22,420
Be careful.

461
00:24:22,450 --> 00:24:23,180
Don't worry.

462
00:24:23,190 --> 00:24:24,320
Even if I get caught,

463
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:26,920
I'll say I climbed over the wall by myself.

464
00:24:27,810 --> 00:24:28,410
Thank you.

465
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:00,360
Monster.

466
00:25:00,700 --> 00:25:01,590
Let's tell them.

467
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:02,120
Monster.

468
00:25:02,180 --> 00:25:03,910
We should have spoken earlier.

469
00:25:04,700 --> 00:25:06,900
If we spoke when we recognized that osmanthus tree on the first day,

470
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:09,460
we might be on our way back now.

471
00:25:10,300 --> 00:25:11,100
Even if we did,

472
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:13,510
will the monster let us go?

473
00:25:14,460 --> 00:25:15,300
Don't forget,

474
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:17,220
we witnessed

475
00:25:17,220 --> 00:25:19,950
how Xue Kuan was torn into pieces by that monster.

476
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,490
Don't mention Xue Kuan.

477
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:22,430
He accidentally

478
00:25:22,490 --> 00:25:24,890
found the Pagoda of Bliss when he was drunk.

479
00:25:25,130 --> 00:25:26,720
Just because he coveted the treasures inside,

480
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:27,810
he incited us to transport the treasures together.

481
00:25:27,810 --> 00:25:29,180
That's why we went there.

482
00:25:29,180 --> 00:25:31,240
But we only transported a few pieces,

483
00:25:31,460 --> 00:25:33,540
went in and out a few times,

484
00:25:33,940 --> 00:25:34,500
and we saw

485
00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:37,320
he was bitten to death by the monster.

486
00:25:37,970 --> 00:25:39,380
That robe floated

487
00:25:39,660 --> 00:25:41,190
behind that monster.

488
00:25:41,600 --> 00:25:43,870
A voice also threatened us

489
00:25:44,210 --> 00:25:46,670
not to leak the secret of the Pagoda of Bliss.

490
00:25:46,930 --> 00:25:49,000
We've kept our mouth shut for so many years

491
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:50,420
and we've been safe.

492
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:51,850
Look.

493
00:25:52,350 --> 00:25:53,550
The monster appeared

494
00:25:53,740 --> 00:25:55,140
as soon as we got here.

495
00:25:56,510 --> 00:25:57,740
Let's not talk about it.

496
00:25:57,740 --> 00:25:58,940
Most of the treasures

497
00:25:59,540 --> 00:26:01,970
were taken away by the Imperial City Division.

498
00:26:01,970 --> 00:26:04,430
We only hid a few pieces and brought them out.

499
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:06,630
All these years, we never dared to sell them.

500
00:26:06,630 --> 00:26:08,040
I only sold one,

501
00:26:08,740 --> 00:26:11,070
and someone found out and brought us here.

502
00:26:11,430 --> 00:26:13,130
It's all my fault.

503
00:26:16,700 --> 00:26:17,560
Let's tell him.

504
00:26:19,280 --> 00:26:20,810
But what about the monster?

505
00:26:21,020 --> 00:26:22,840
Although it's scary,

506
00:26:23,580 --> 00:26:25,260
it will only kill us.

507
00:26:25,460 --> 00:26:26,980
But the Wansheng Clan

508
00:26:26,980 --> 00:26:28,780
can do anything.

509
00:26:28,930 --> 00:26:30,530
For the safety of our family,

510
00:26:31,260 --> 00:26:32,810
we can sacrifice our lives.

511
00:26:34,150 --> 00:26:34,950
It's worth it.

512
00:26:35,570 --> 00:26:36,900
Now that you mention it,

513
00:26:37,860 --> 00:26:38,850
I remember now.

514
00:26:39,380 --> 00:26:42,020
There was an osmanthus tree

515
00:26:42,630 --> 00:26:45,060
a few meters away from the entrance.

516
00:26:45,630 --> 00:26:46,360
Based on

517
00:26:46,780 --> 00:26:48,150
the osmanthus trees

518
00:26:48,170 --> 00:26:49,440
we saw these days,

519
00:26:50,120 --> 00:26:52,720
the entrance is probably

520
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,000
here.

521
00:27:15,420 --> 00:27:17,750
It turns out that it is tied to a black kite.

522
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:20,760
No wonder it floats so strangely.

523
00:27:23,540 --> 00:27:24,060
Oh no.

524
00:27:26,100 --> 00:27:29,810
[Shanyi Workshop]

525
00:27:38,020 --> 00:27:38,880
What happened?

526
00:27:39,820 --> 00:27:40,830
Tell them

527
00:27:41,550 --> 00:27:42,880
not to kill my family.

528
00:27:43,510 --> 00:27:45,240
I... I'll tell you everything.

529
00:27:45,660 --> 00:27:47,060
The Pagoda of Bliss is...

530
00:27:47,220 --> 00:27:47,850
Is...

531
00:27:55,310 --> 00:27:56,710
The governor has ordered

532
00:27:56,870 --> 00:28:01,000
that those who break into the inner palace shall be executed immediately.

533
00:28:02,350 --> 00:28:04,560
What should we do with this thief?

534
00:28:10,150 --> 00:28:11,010
Sect Leader Li,

535
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:12,780
how can I protect you?

536
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:16,070
Lord Yang, do not feel conflicted.

537
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,160
Do as you must.

538
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:20,250
[Grand Court]

539
00:28:24,460 --> 00:28:26,900
Breaking into the inner palace at night is a serious crime.

540
00:28:26,900 --> 00:28:28,700
There is no point in struggling.

541
00:28:28,700 --> 00:28:29,960
If you admit the murder,

542
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:31,540
you may be cleared of some crimes

543
00:28:31,540 --> 00:28:32,870
and die less painfully.

544
00:28:33,050 --> 00:28:34,510
The Grand Court's tactics

545
00:28:35,950 --> 00:28:38,080
are much worse than Baichuan Court's.

546
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:40,790
My lord.

547
00:28:40,940 --> 00:28:43,220
Lord Yang Yunchun from the Imperial City Division wants to visit again.

548
00:28:43,220 --> 00:28:43,740
No.

549
00:28:44,250 --> 00:28:45,310
This man is a felon.

550
00:28:45,580 --> 00:28:47,240
No one is allowed to visit him.

551
00:28:51,410 --> 00:28:52,210
You may leave.

552
00:28:52,660 --> 00:28:53,030
Yes.

553
00:28:57,800 --> 00:28:59,500
It's fine if you don't admit it.

554
00:28:59,500 --> 00:29:01,220
It doesn't matter anymore.

555
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:04,100
Master thinks you're too troublesome,

556
00:29:04,220 --> 00:29:05,790
so I'll kill you now.

557
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:39,920
Charge!

558
00:29:40,510 --> 00:29:41,090
Stop!

559
00:29:43,460 --> 00:29:45,190
The Empress Dowager's decree!

560
00:29:50,280 --> 00:29:53,220
There are many suspicious points about Li Lianhua's trespassing.

561
00:29:53,220 --> 00:29:54,460
He may be wrongfully accused.

562
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:56,960
You are appointed to assist Baichuan Court's Detective Fang Duobing

563
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,670
to investigate this case

564
00:29:59,020 --> 00:30:00,220
and redeem yourself.

565
00:30:04,900 --> 00:30:05,820
Leave now!

