575
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,410
Calm down.

576
00:30:30,900 --> 00:30:32,370
Actually, there's another advantage

577
00:30:32,370 --> 00:30:33,420
to me being here.

578
00:30:33,940 --> 00:30:34,800
It happens that

579
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:36,180
