581
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:41,740
I don't want to argue with you,

582
00:30:42,350 --> 00:30:43,610
as long as you're safe.

583
00:30:43,660 --> 00:30:44,260
By the way,

584
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:47,230
I heard Shan Gudao came to the imperial city.

585
00:30:47,230 --> 00:30:49,360
I'm afraid it's for the mother bug too.

586
00:30:50,260 --> 00:30:50,900
I

587
00:30:51,660 --> 00:30:53,220
met him a few times.

