594
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:07,940
There must be a third person behind this.

595
00:31:07,940 --> 00:31:09,180
He did all this

596
00:31:09,540 --> 00:31:10,260
to stop all the people

597
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:11,980
who want to find the Pagoda of Bliss.

598
00:31:11,980 --> 00:31:12,780
That's right.

599
00:31:12,930 --> 00:31:14,190
It's just as I guessed.

600
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:17,630
Did you find anything else?

