603
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:26,370
I thought about it for a long time but couldn't figure it out.

604
00:31:26,370 --> 00:31:27,800
But now I finally know

605
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:29,980
what this circle means.

606
00:31:30,700 --> 00:31:31,280
What?

607
00:31:31,870 --> 00:31:32,370
A well.

608
00:31:34,780 --> 00:31:35,700
You mean

609
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:38,180
the entrance to the Pagoda of Bliss

