611
00:31:40,740 --> 00:31:41,860
But if such a pagoda

612
00:31:41,980 --> 00:31:43,150
is still in the palace,

613
00:31:43,150 --> 00:31:44,700
someone would have discovered it.

614
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:46,390
I haven't figured it out yet.

615
00:31:47,080 --> 00:31:48,610
But the only thing we know is

616
00:31:49,040 --> 00:31:50,200
the four were killed

617
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:53,920
and Shan Gudao has lost the clue to the pagoda.

618
00:31:55,070 --> 00:31:56,670
The third person behind this

619
00:31:57,320 --> 00:32:00,250
stops others from searching for the Pagoda of Bliss,

620
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:03,060
