00:33:19,090 --> 00:33:19,730
No poison?

643
00:33:20,250 --> 00:33:22,650
It doesn't make sense if there's no poison.

644
00:33:22,940 --> 00:33:24,520
Could the Ni Tianhou be real

645
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,890
