646
00:33:27,700 --> 00:33:30,160
Maybe the poison isn't in the food and water.

647
00:33:31,690 --> 00:33:33,770
There was such an osmanthus tree

648
00:33:34,080 --> 00:33:35,830
a few meters away from the entrance.

649
00:33:35,830 --> 00:33:36,980
Based on the osmanthus trees

650
00:33:36,980 --> 00:33:38,700
we saw these days,

651
00:33:39,540 --> 00:33:40,270
the entrance

652
00:33:41,060 --> 00:33:41,950
is probably

653
00:33:43,530 --> 00:33:44,620
in this position.

654
00:33:54,150 --> 00:33:54,860
The map.

655
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:58,080
It should be the map

656
00:33:58,570 --> 00:33:59,880
that they checked.

657
00:34:00,420 --> 00:34:01,550
The poison was on it.

658
00:34:01,700 --> 00:34:02,700
After reading it,

659
00:34:02,890 --> 00:34:04,110
