00:34:15,820 --> 00:34:18,020
Since the beast is real

667
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:19,719
and Ni Tianhou is fake,

668
00:34:20,060 --> 00:34:21,500
then can't we find it

669
00:34:21,520 --> 00:34:22,610
by tracing this smell?

