718
00:37:25,780 --> 00:37:26,460
I see.

719
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:28,720
The Beast Garden?

720
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:29,660
That's right.

721
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:30,870
Let's go.

722
00:37:31,980 --> 00:37:32,640
Uncle Qian,

723
00:37:33,570 --> 00:37:34,500
long time no see.

724
00:37:35,820 --> 00:37:36,730
Fang,

725
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:39,480
long time no see. You've grown up.

