00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:30,360
until it reached five kilograms.

748
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:33,200
This went on for seven or eight years.

749
00:38:35,250 --> 00:38:37,180
Then it became one kilogram again.

750
00:38:37,530 --> 00:38:38,730
This kept repeating.

751
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:40,320
It's very strange.

