00:40:05,770 --> 00:40:07,590
Instead, they went to Shanyi Workshop.

798
00:40:07,590 --> 00:40:08,220
Before this,

799
00:40:08,220 --> 00:40:10,260
I thought it was done by the Shan Gudao alone,

