00:40:53,650 --> 00:40:55,710
Shan Gudao lost Li Fei and the others.

819
00:40:56,020 --> 00:40:57,680
If he wants to find the Pagoda of Bliss,

820
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:58,810
his only clue

821
00:40:59,100 --> 00:41:00,460
